{
  "stem": "142.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, put them together as a pair, and take it in your hand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And walk in through the corridor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Come into the-- before going into the gas chamber, you had to leave it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Somebody was taking them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, my-- my first observations of that is that I saw 25 to 3,000 people going on the-- on the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they close the doors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, you know, then I knew that the SS threw the Zyklon B, you know, from above-- three, four openings.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when-- you know, it takes about four, five minutes to die.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Except the people that are in front where the gas is coming, there, it takes some out a couple of minutes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And after-- after that, you know, when-- after 15, 20 minutes-- they open up the thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The first thing I see, I saw the people who I saw 15 minutes before alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I saw the mothers with their children standing up before-- because the gas chamber will-- will take maybe 500 people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It used to make 2,500 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Everybody standing up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was no room for anything else but standing up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when you see that, after-- it's, you know, some, there are black and blues from the gas.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- it's something that, I said to myself, how can you-- somebody be able to survive in such an environment?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, the first thing they did, they gave us a-- a pair of scissors to start cutting their hair.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, where do you go?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You start at one, two, then I have to put my-- my foot on top of somebody's stomach.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- from the gas, I heard a ah!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Big-- so I jump up 100 meters away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said to myself, how can I-- how can I do it?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
